TrustedCoin,is,a,bitcoin,security,service,that,offers,to,add,additional,levels,of,security,and,authentication,to,bitcoin,storage,and,transactions,The,TrustedCoin,API,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,JSON,The,API,allows,users,to,send,alerts,to,prevent,unauthorized,transactions,create,custom,wallets,and,add,additional,layers,of,security,on,top,of,bitcoin,wallets,and,other,services,An,account,is,required,with,service